The People of the State of Illinois, defendant in error, v. Adam Bartosh, plaintiff in error.Gen. No. 31,129.Heard in the third division of this court for the first district at the October term, 1926.

Taylor, J., dissents.

Opinion filed March 2, 1927.Jacob Levy, for plaintiff in error. Robert E. Crowe, State’s Attorney, for defendant in error; Clarence E. Nelson and Edward E. Wilson, Assistant State’s Attorneys, of counsel. Mr. Justice O’Connor

delivered the opinion of the court.
